WEBVTT

00:01.384 --> 00:03.484
I was thinking that
maybe I could help fix up

00:03.551 --> 00:06.319
Matt and Gwen's place in
exchange for staying there.

00:06.353 --> 00:07.921
You want to sleep in the
house where Matt was killed?

00:07.955 --> 00:11.658
- Are you sure you want to... stay here?
- Yeah.

00:11.692 --> 00:13.026
I do.

00:13.060 --> 00:14.594
Sibila: You said you'd send for us.

00:14.628 --> 00:17.230
You're too busy hustling to be there for me,

00:17.264 --> 00:19.032
for your own daughter?

00:19.066 --> 00:20.099
Hector: You want me to talk on Carter?

00:20.134 --> 00:22.602
I'm not saying nothing until
I know you're for real.

00:22.636 --> 00:23.703
What kind of gesture?

00:23.737 --> 00:25.672
Get me someplace I'm protected.

00:25.706 --> 00:26.840
Juvie ain't nothing.

00:26.874 --> 00:28.608
Hang close, do how I do,

00:28.642 --> 00:31.010
and you'll be out of here in no time.

00:31.045 --> 00:32.846
- Hello, mom.
- It's "mom" now, hmm?

00:32.880 --> 00:35.348
Your father... God bless
him... is an enabler. I'm not.

00:35.382 --> 00:37.016
I've never tolerated the
things that you've done.

00:37.051 --> 00:39.819
I need you to get this to somebody.

00:40.888 --> 00:43.790
[Chuckles]

00:43.824 --> 00:45.425
The prosecutor making this a hate crime

00:45.459 --> 00:46.526
was punitive, not real.

00:46.560 --> 00:49.762
- You want confrontation.
- We want a fair examination.

00:49.797 --> 00:50.763
- Man: What do we want?
- Justice!

00:50.798 --> 00:51.764
- When do we want it?
- Now!

00:51.799 --> 00:52.832
- What do we want?
- Justice!

00:52.867 --> 00:54.400
Man: [Amplified] <i>You are
unlawfully assembled.</i>

00:54.435 --> 00:56.469
- <i>Disperse immediately! Now!
- Justice!</i>

00:56.503 --> 00:58.071
[Explosion] <i>Surge!</i>

00:58.105 --> 00:59.572
[Women screaming]

00:59.607 --> 01:01.374
Go, go, go, go!

01:01.408 --> 01:02.942
Barb: I think I want a gun.

01:02.977 --> 01:03.943
Ben: For what purpose?

01:03.978 --> 01:05.444
[Sighs] Self-protection.

01:05.479 --> 01:06.813
Try this one. It's a revolver.

01:06.847 --> 01:07.814
[Trigger clicks]

01:07.848 --> 01:09.649
I'll take it.

01:09.683 --> 01:11.484
Remember,

01:11.518 --> 01:14.287
finger off the trigger till
you're ready to shoot.

01:14.321 --> 01:16.489
W-whoa, whoa.

01:16.523 --> 01:19.492
Always keep it pointed downrange.

01:19.526 --> 01:21.661
Position.

01:21.695 --> 01:25.298
Remember, front sight.

01:25.332 --> 01:26.099
Center of mass.

01:26.133 --> 01:27.467
Press the weapon into the target.

01:27.501 --> 01:30.270
Lean just a little bit.

01:30.304 --> 01:32.639
All right, trigger when ready.

01:32.673 --> 01:35.108
Press smoothly to the rear.

01:40.948 --> 01:42.916
Yeah.

01:42.950 --> 01:44.751
Keep going.

01:51.158 --> 01:53.159
[Gunshots]

02:00.801 --> 02:03.636
[Gun clicks]

02:03.671 --> 02:06.205
[Gun thuds]

02:06.240 --> 02:09.142
You want to see how you did?

02:14.882 --> 02:17.216
All the shots to the head
and the body are kill shots.

02:17.251 --> 02:18.184
That's good, right?

02:18.218 --> 02:22.021
Well, if your intention
was to shoot to kill,

02:22.056 --> 02:24.457
that's very good.

02:24.491 --> 02:25.825
Want to do it again?

02:25.859 --> 02:27.493
Yeah.

